									<td><strong>#sydney supermeet!</strong><br>Calling ALL Sydney IRC users!!! #sydney is having a Super Meet! We are currently in the process of discussing venues, and numbers. If you wish to find out more information about this meet then please go to Sydney forums read this <A HREF="http://forum.sydneyirc.com/showthread.php?s=&threadid=354" target=_blank>thread</A> and let people know that you are interested, or if you have a suggestion for a venue, then by all means!! suggest away! This is a good chance for those who know the nicks but not the faces to come along and say hello! More details will be posted as they are finalised. <br><div class=newscredits>September 24th 3:41pm, Submitted by <a href="mailto:lolly@austnet.org">Lolly</a></div></td></tr>
