									<td valign=top><a name="26"><img src="../images/dot_orange.gif" height="8" width="8" vspace="5"></a></td>
									<td><strong>#PicturePoll meet a huge success</strong><br>On April 13th the regulars from <A HREF="http://www.picturepoll.com/" target=_blank>#picturepoll</A> headed to Albert Park for their first meet since last year's successful meet. Organisers set up the BBQ, got out the food and drinks .. and it started to rain! Organisers feared that noone would turn up. By a couple of hours later, 30 people had turned up, everyone was laughing and the BBQ was a huge success. Pictures can be viewed <A HREF="http://www.picturepoll.com/meet/bbq2/" target=_blank>HERE</a>. The organisers would like to thank all the people that came, and are looking forward to the next meet!<br><div class=newscredits>April 22nd 12:06pm, Submitted by <a href="mailto:cetin@picturepoll.com">Cetin</a></div></td></tr>
<table width="100%" cellpadding=2>
								<tr>
									<td valign=top><a name="25"><img src="../images/dot_orange.gif" height="8" width="8" vspace="5"></a></td>
									<td><strong>#Bifemsex channel meet</strong><br>One of the more R-rated channels on Austnet, #Bifemsex has a channel meet in Sydney on 24th April at the Bank Hotel, Newtown, 7:30 pm. More details can be found at the <A HREF=http://www.bifemsexchat.com/ target=_blank>channel website</a>, or by asking in the channel. <br><div class=newscredits>April 15th 12:04pm, Submitted by <a href="mailto:pornie69@hotmail.com">`aMYBaby</a></div></td></tr>
<table width="100%" cellpadding=2>
